                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      Committee believes that Alcon&#8217;s &#8220;unaffected share price&#8221; is significantly
      greater than Novartis contends.</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Alcon&#8217;s
      share price rose steadily throughout 2009; while Novartis asserts that
      this was driven by speculation in Alcon&#8217;s shares, it coincided with
      positive earnings surprises in every quarter and progressively increasing
      future earnings expectations among analysts (see attached
      annex).</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Alcon
      has seen no appreciable spikes in trading volume, which might indicate
      speculation, other than on a single date in December when an equity
      analyst wrote a report about a potential
  squeeze-out.</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      report was preceded by comments from Novartis CFO Raymund Breu on October
      22, 2009 indicating no plans to execute a squeeze-out of the minority
      shareholders.</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><br></div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      Committee believes that the analysis that Novartis employs to support its
      assertion that Alcon&#8217;s unaffected share price is US$137 is fundamentally
      flawed.</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Novartis&#8217;
      &#8220;Methodology 1&#8221; asserts that Alcon should trade at a similar or lower
      price-to-earnings ratio than it did in April 2008 (prior to the
      announcement of the Nestl&#233;/Novartis
  transaction).&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div align="left">
                                                                                                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                              <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                              <td>
                                                                                                                                <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">However,
      Novartis calculates the 2010E price-to-earnings ratio as of April 2008
      (i.e. a 3-year forward multiple) and applies that same multiple to 2010E
      expected earnings today (i.e., a 1-year forward earnings estimate),
      </font><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">ignoring
      the fact that nearly two years have passed since April 2008, and that
      3-year forward multiples are typically lower than 1-year forward multiples
      for high-growth companies.</font></div>
                                                                                                                              </td>
                                                                                                                            </tr></table>
                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                      <div>
                                                                                                                        <div><br>
                                                                                                                          <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">

                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">For
      instance, in the Novartis example, Alcon traded at the following forward
      multiples of earnings as of April 2008 (note that each successive year
      results in a 2x &#8211; 3x multiple decline due to higher earnings expectations
      year-over-year)<font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 70%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: text-top">1</font>:</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                      <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 180pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">2008E
      (1-year forward multiple) &#8211; 22.7x</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">2009E
      (2-year forward multiple ) &#8211; 19.8x</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>

                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">2010E
      (3-year forward multiple ) &#8211; 17.7x</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>

                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">2011E
      (4-year forward multiple ) &#8211; 15.8x</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                      <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Novartis
      should have applied multiples across comparable time periods (e.g., the
      one-year forward 2008 multiple in April 2008 should now be applied to
      Alcon&#8217;s (one-year forward) 2010 earnings
  estimate).</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                      <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Correcting
      Novartis&#8217; analysis in this fashion produces a range of unaffected stock
      prices that approximates the US$164.35 closing price of Alcon on December
      31, 2009.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                      <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Nor
      do we agree (for reasons enumerated under the first bullet point above)
      that Alcon should have experienced the same multiple contraction as other
      healthcare companies have experienced since April
  2008.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>
                                                                                                                              </div>
                                                                                                                              <div>
                                                                                                                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                      <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                      <td>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Novartis&#8217;
      &#8220;Methodology 2&#8221;&#160;asserts that Alcon should trade in line with a number
      of broad healthcare stock indices, ignoring the fact that since its IPO in
      2002, Alcon has consistently outperformed every one of the 12 indices that
      Novartis cited.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </td>
                                                                                                                                    </tr></table>

Performance of Alcon versus Healthcare Indices<font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 70%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: text-top">2</font></font></font></div>
                                                                                                                                  <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">March

<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Since
      the time of Alcon&#8217;s IPO (or the inception of the index, if more recent) to
      April 4, 2008, Alcon outperformed the indices by over 20 percentage points
      on a compound annual basis, on
average.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>

                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      market has consistently rewarded Alcon with a premium valuation because of
      the reasons discussed under the first bullet point
  above.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Novartis&#8217;
      &#8220;Methodology 3&#8221; selectively chooses comments from the equity analyst
      community in an attempt to demonstrate support for Novartis&#8217; view,
      highlighting three analysts (of 12 who cover Alcon) who discussed an
      unaffected share price that approximates US$137, while ignoring these same
      analysts&#8217; views of the appropriate price to be paid for the minority
      shares.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>

<tr style="TEXT-ALIGN: center;">
                                                                                                                                    <td valign="bottom" width="191" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 2px">
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; TEXT-DECORATION: underline">Analysts
      Cited by Novartis</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td valign="bottom" width="222" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 2px">
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">Reference
      to</font></div>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; TEXT-DECORATION: underline">Takeout
      Price</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td valign="bottom" width="213">
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt">
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">Synergy</font></div>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="center"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; TEXT-DECORATION: underline">Estimate</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      </div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr><tr>
                                                                                                                                    <td valign="top" width="191" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left">
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">BMO
      Capital Markets</font></div>

                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Moreover,
      7 of the 8 analysts (including the three cited by Novartis) who express a
      view on the expected Novartis squeeze-out price cite prices of US$181 or
      greater.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><br></div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Based
      on input from Alcon&#8217;s management, the Committee believes that Novartis has
      understated achievable synergies in the transaction, by failing to
      quantify the significant revenue synergies that
      exist.&#160;&#160;Additionally, Novartis has overstated its ability to
      realize cost synergies absent a full combination and Novartis does not
      accord the minority shareholders <font style="DISPLAY: inline; TEXT-DECORATION: underline">any</font> synergy
      value.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">In
      addition to the US$300 million of cost synergies cited by Novartis, the
      Committee believes that there is an even greater amount of revenue
      synergies, none of which appear to be reflected in the Novartis
      proposal.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      Committee does not believe that Novartis can achieve two-thirds of the
      potential synergies without total ownership of
  Alcon:</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">

                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">

                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Co-promotion
      or other agreements would require arms-length negotiations and approval of
      the Committee; and</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 108pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Wingdings">&#167;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Novartis
      could not fully rationalize sales forces or back office
      functions.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><br></div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">The
      Committee disagrees with Novartis&#8217; assertion that a 12% premium to the
      unaffected share price is &#8220;very much in line with what minority
      shareholders in similar transactions have
  received.&#8221;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">A
      review of 247 squeeze-out transactions announced over the past decade with
      a value greater than US$100 million showed that the final premium paid for
      the minority shares over the share price one week and one month prior to
      announcement were 27% and 30% on average, respectively, with median values
      of 18% and 21%, respectively.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                    <td>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Indeed,
      Novartis itself set a precedent in 2005 when they paid a premium of
      approximately 25% to the unaffected price to squeeze-out the minority
      shareholders of Eon Labs, which also represented a premium of 9% to the
      price they paid for their majority
stake.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>

                                                                                                                                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                            <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                              <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                            <td>
                                                                                                                                              <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">In
      addition to undervaluing Alcon&#8217;s minority shares, the Committee views the
      terms of the Novartis proposal as inferior to the terms offered to Alcon&#8217;s
      current majority shareholder.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                          </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                                    <div>
                                                                                                                                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                            <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                              <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                            <td>
                                                                                                                                              <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Minority
      shareholders are to receive stock consideration, whereas Nestl&#233; is to
      receive cash.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                          </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                                    <div>
                                                                                                                                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                            <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                              <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                            <td>
                                                                                                                                              <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Stock
      consideration is offered at a fixed exchange ratio, which creates
      uncertainty as to the value to be ultimately received by the minority
      shareholders.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                          </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                                    <div>
                                                                                                                                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                            <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 72pt">
                                                                                                                                              <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">o&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                            <td>
                                                                                                                                              <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">In
      spite of the stock-based consideration, the Novartis merger proposal is
      likely to be taxable for United States income tax
  purposes.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                            </td>
                                                                                                                                          </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                                    <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><br></div>
                                                                                                                                    <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Annex:
Unaffected Share Price Analysis</font></div>
                                                                                                                                    <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify">
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Fundamental
Drivers of Alcon&#8217;s Share Price Performance</font></div>
                                                                                                                                      <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify">
                                                                                                                                        <div>
                                                                                                                                          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                                <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                                  <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                </td>
                                                                                                                                                <td>
                                                                                                                                                  <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Evidence
      does not support the contention that a large speculative premium was
      imbedded in Alcon stock prior to the announcement of the Novartis
      proposal</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                </td>
                                                                                                                                              </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                        </div>
                                                                                                                                        <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify">
                                                                                                                                          <div>
                                                                                                                                            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                                  <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 36pt">
                                                                                                                                                    <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                  </td>
                                                                                                                                                  <td>
                                                                                                                                                    <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Alcon
      shares have steadily risen in 2009 in conjunction with strong earnings
      announcements and several strategic transaction
    announcements</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                  </td>
                                                                                                                                                </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                          </div>
                                                                                                                                          <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify">
                                                                                                                                            <div>
                                                                                                                                              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
                                                                                                                                                    <td align="right" style="WIDTH: 48px">
                                                                                                                                                      <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt;" face="Symbol, serif">&#183;&#160;</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                                    <td width="1062">
                                                                                                                                                      <div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Additionally,
      a high correlation between Alcon&#8217;s share price change and changes in
      street earnings would imply that research analyst earnings revisions
      (along with Alcon&#8217;s results) appear to have driven the share price
      performance, in both directions, since early
  2008</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                    </td>
                                                                                                                                                  </tr></table>
                                                                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                                                                            <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img src="acl6k0120idcex9919.jpg" alt=""></div>
                                                                                                                                            <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
                                                                                                                                              <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left"><br><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Note: Last
day of data as of 12/31/2009.</font></div>
                                                                                                                                              <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">(1) 2010E
EPS estimates are per FactSet and indexed as of 1/1/08</font></div>

                                                                                                                                                  <div><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">About
Alcon</font></div>
                                                                                                                                                </div>
                                                                                                                                                <div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
                                                                                                                                                  <div style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">Alcon,
Inc. is the world&#8217;s leading eye care company, with sales of approximately $6.3
billion in 2008.&#160;&#160;Alcon, which has been dedicated to the ophthalmic
industry for 65 years, researches, develops, manufactures and markets
pharmaceuticals, surgical equipment and devices, contacts lens solutions and
other vision care products that treat diseases, disorders and other conditions
of the eye.&#160;&#160;Alcon operates in 75 countries and sells products in 180
markets.&#160;&#160;For more information on Alcon, Inc., visit the Company&#8217;s web
site at www.alcon.com.</font></div>
